Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为了一己野心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把骨肉献祭给妖怪的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为了取回被夺走的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爬出黑暗深渊的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,于建立在其牺牲之上得以繁荣的醍醐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻两人初次会面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸还不知道那火焰的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不自觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被引导至此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是  谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,板门之卷  下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这位大人岂能让你随口发问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不知道领主醍醐景光大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不得好死的孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,追  追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,殿下  还是先撤回府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你  还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这边  别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不得好死的孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是  不得好死的  孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙  放开我  放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,助六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,臭小孩真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,放开助六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是来见他母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,少啰嗦  越过板门的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是妖怪之国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪之国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,助六
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧  有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没能回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,家  已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他说全村人  都被杀光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲也  肯定被…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,助六  没事  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  不是还有我在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸哥哥肯定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们一起去云游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心  醍醐之民有观世音菩萨保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,观世音菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  那些朝仓的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会被一张板门阻挡也是因此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,板门上依附着鬼神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓的士兵是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么妖怪之国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,讨伐醍醐之国者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才是妖魔鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,必将遭到天罚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  那家纹  好像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是醍醐家纹  同时也是旗印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  有洞穴  和外界相通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太狭窄了行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,助六我们逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在这里会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  死掉就可以见到母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  遇到这点小事就气馁怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么高行不通的  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能在这种地方丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经发誓不再输给武士了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,助六  等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会带着大哥哥来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少主  不要冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人可还记得手脚 眼睛 鼻子 耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全都被妖怪所吞噬的婴儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,十六年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人和母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,将其献祭给妖怪的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一刻也未曾忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,臭小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}喂  有人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,放开  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,助六
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,将婴儿扔进了河里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为了国家  将一无所知的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这还算是为人父母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是父母应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,过去这个地狱般国家的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,接二连三的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,流行病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天地异变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有周围虎视眈眈的小国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,风烛残年般的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为和鬼神的约定才得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人不为国家的富足高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不是为了人民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道不是为了父亲的野心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,领主的利益就是人民的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为此牺牲的不是别人而是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,作为武士没有什么好丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,歹人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不得好死的孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,陆奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,兵库
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,您受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为了哥哥要献出这个国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不想背负任何痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只一味保持自己的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想把人民再推进地狱之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就去那间地狱堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去和鬼神们解除约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话哥哥的身体就会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,国家也会毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不得好死的孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥快跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,助六他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,已经决定作为向醍醐宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,将你们钉到板门上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,板门的鬼怪好像已经被赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也终于可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大人也终于下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,连这些老人和伤员都被找来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓有这么多军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,宅邸那边出现了可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么领主杀死的鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然被封印的只有这一只
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但这怎么看都很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我这糟老头子可以应付的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他是怎么负担这么多鬼神的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道谁给你起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但就像知道他的经历一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这看起来不像要打仗的景象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是要保护这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但把哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但这也太惨无人道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好我们的立场无法回答这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们兄弟在小时候就成为了敌人的俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是醍醐的壮大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在也不会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟百鬼丸好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,列队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个鬼神像的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也有没伤痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大人和鬼神的约定正在逐渐被破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被哥哥破坏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说起醍醐景光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里的一国之君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他的家纹和大哥哥的护身符上的是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那位夫人叫大哥哥什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,助六的妈妈已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,助六不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要赶在他被钉到板门上之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,少主 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不想背负任何痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只一味保持自己的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想把人民再推进地狱之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不必再惧怕板门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,作为我们朝仓问候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能再等大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看来因果的齿轮转回原点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,作为见证人也是因果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只能祈祷的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么干出这种蠢事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是板门的妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大人 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是妖怪干的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就是大哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,果…果然是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他把我的手臂砍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为命令 我才迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫多宝丸 是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 我说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲对你的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为这是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然让鬼神吃掉自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,由此使国家繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不得好死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是他让大哥哥变成这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我的父亲 醍醐景光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,做到如此地步也是为了保护国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在打破与鬼神的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,国家就会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在威胁国家安危的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,才是鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好 多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以前来 讨伐你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,助六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,绑得真紧啊 怎么都解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有大哥哥的刀 一下子就切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妖狐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,狐狸妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,被板门吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸 想必你很怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,恨那天没能保护你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那让鬼神吃掉你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那过得逍遥自在的醍醐人民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥…大哥哥他活得多么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,连多宝丸都懂的道理 你什么时候能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我…不能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你怎样恢复人形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就算了解你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这样 我们国家也要乞求你的宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们国家只能不断蚕食着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会只让你一人牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你们还想要人体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就取我的命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,陆奥 兵库
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保护夫人和多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 助六 快逃
